OL,5,G1125 Fern Britton: Inside the Vet's
OL,6,     FFern meets a Jack Russell terrier
OL,7,     Fwhose enormous lump is proving to
OL,8,     Fbe a puzzle for the vets, while a
OL,9,     F10-month-old cat is brought in
OL,10,     Fwith an injury sustained in a
OL,11,     Ffight. Dr James Greenwood provides
OL,12,     Femergency care to a whippet with a
OL,13,     Fnasty throat injury, and also
OL,14,     Fdelivers a masterclass on doggy
OL,15,     Fdental hygiene with special help
OL,16,     Ffrom his own pet Dolly
